<main class="shell page-grid reveal">
  <section class="content-flow">
    <p class="eyebrow">Contact</p>
    <h2>This page provides a simple way to present contact information within the portfolio structure.</h2>
    <p>It is meant to be straightforward. If someone wanted to ask about coursework, projects, or future collaboration, the information here would give them a place to start.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="content-flow">
    <h3>Contact details</h3>
    <p><strong>Email:</strong> <%= studio.mentor.email %></p>
    <p><strong>Focus area:</strong> <%= studio.mentor.focus %></p>
    <p><strong>Best time to connect:</strong> <%= studio.officeHours[0] %></p>
  </section>

  <section class="content-flow statement-band">
    <p class="eyebrow">Submission note</p>
    <p>For the assignment post, I would mention that the site uses the Open-Meteo API and the <code>@faker-js/faker</code> package, and then deploy the project so other students can review it.</p>
  </section>
</main>

